<doc id="639163" wikidata="Q8039239" url="?curid=639163" title="Wunda">
<text>Wunda is a dark spirit in Indigenous Australian aboriginal mythology.

Wunda may also refer to:
* Wunda (crater), an enigmatic bright feature on Uranus&#x27;s moon Umbriel.</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q170355" start="26" end="47" title="Indigenous Australian" label="Indigenous Australian"/>
<link wikidata="Q376608" start="48" end="68" title="aboriginal mythology" label="aboriginal mythology"/>
<link wikidata="Q2730338" start="98" end="112" title="Wunda (crater)" label="Wunda (crater)"/>
